Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hi, everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, please \Nkeep your room brightly lit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you ever created \Nsomething with your friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Working hard toward the same goal,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}cooperating with all sorts of people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and helping each other makes you feel good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please support our new show. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please support! Please support!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be someplace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be somewhere {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember how I used to say \NI could make it to the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must have been pretending to be tough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I did was reckless \Nand it never got me anywhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you alone were always beside me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be somewhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can start going forward {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this moment, something will start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light I haven't seen yet is \Nbeaming toward the promised place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how time passes by so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been two weeks \Nsince we moved in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, not only are we far from \Ncreating our own Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also we have no jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told my mother and father \Nnot to worry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could practice someplace a \Nlittle bigger than here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope something like a dream happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. Something like a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... It's like a dream all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd try combining tightrope \Nwalking and the cushion throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Mia, Anna, please make \Nsure no one sees your panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all girls here. So who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\i1}no{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do if a peeping Tom \Nor a perverted spirit is watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a perverted spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:15.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Amazing Change From Zero to Hero."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Yuri's Kaleido Stage is to \Nface the colorful opening date today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the trouble to send \Ninvitations. It means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... This could be a challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage has been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show we're aiming at is a fantastic \Nshow which has never existed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the revolutionary flame is \Nready to blaze up in entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they spent a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he did this \Nto rub it in our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I co-starred with Miss Layla on that stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone did their best, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we received enthusiastic \Napplause from the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... this is no longer our Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like I was in an amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought Miss Layla might be here also.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume she also got an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she could be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she's doing another \Nmovie. It was in the magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's not doing stage shows anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't see that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri, can I have your autograph, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Wait one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to take a chance and rent \Nthe Empire Stage for $350 a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we rent it for three days, we'll be broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we can find a place much cheaper \Nand rent the place for at least ten days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our reputation will not have time to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find a good job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wanted: performers to participate in the \Ngrand opening of a giant seafood restaurant."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They pay pretty well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it says that you have to audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're more than happy to audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you want to try their audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it. Everyone, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the job by all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all we had to do was wear \Nthis and hand out balloons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we didn't need to audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you're in a crab costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, I'm a shrimp. A shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, both of you, motivate \Nyourselves and let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm spinning more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there, there, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing detaining \Ncustomers at the entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let customers go \Ninside the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are supposed to \Nbe delicious ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of doing all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to hand out balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you audition us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, smile, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's taking a \Nlittle time to be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off than I \Nam. 'Cause you're a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, on the other hand, am a shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you tell me to smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try some delicious seafood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so perfect in that costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't help myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri Killian, are you all right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry. I reserved \Nyou a special seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people, we just had \Nto be seen dressed like that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the person we least wanted to be seen by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crab costume would be one \Nthing, but why a shrimp costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked Mr. Policeman, \Nhe told me you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish your training?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing like the "Unryu" style \Nwhen a sumo wrestler parades in the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you go to train for singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? I trained for sumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, seeing your faces calms me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you need to go back to Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? To Kalos? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? 'Cause... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't talked to Kalos in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's taking some time by \Nhimself to think about his future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think? Aren't you worried about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being unfaithful or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to what happened the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out Kalos is still head \Nover heels in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I found you a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wanted: performers to perform on \Nthe open stage at Marine Park"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find \Nthis while I was in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I went to Marine Park, \Nthinking I had nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I was able to sign a \Ntemporary agreement with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's only for one day, \Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The group that is performing right \Nnow suddenly can't perform that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're going to remove \Nthe current set at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this, you don't have \Ntime for rehearsal either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we'll do it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We have no reasons to reject it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can get a good reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they may ask us back next time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, you should take a \Nshower and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I haven't done anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the day after tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't have enough time to \Ncreate anything with a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you want keep it simple \Nand just do a performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wonder if we could contact \Nthe cast members from "Freedom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good idea. I'll e-mail them right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Miss Layla too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should contact Miss \NLayla too. Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla... I don't \Nknow if she's interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But if Sora wants to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Shall we visit Miss Layla's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we want to create a new Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we thought it would be \Nnice if you could join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a camera test for \Nthe movie later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tomorrow, I have a costume fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd have time \Nfor anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, my father is \Nmanaging my schedule right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only do my best in the \Nsituation I'm in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't done your \Nlast show yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:13:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I still want to appear \Non stage with you, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you gain weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you still don't \Nunderstand how hard it is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to get everything back if you \Nskip your training even one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Miss Layla started \Nwalking a different path from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla has her own battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you act now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this three-volume instructional video
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is yours for only $200!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. How was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, Miss Layla cannot do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's disappointing, \Nbut what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got some e-mail responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Elena, Jeanne, Claire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also from Emilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Wow... All of a sudden, \NI'm getting motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's only for one day, \Nwe want to make it the best show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've read your e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go there immediately. Rosetta
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected her to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I sent her an e-mail just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can they do? The rent is cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the performance will \Nbe held the day after tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the open stage at Marine Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your ideas \Non how we can create a show
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we can prepare for in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, I want to get your ideas \Non how we can make the show interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped by to look at \Nthe actual stage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling is lower than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can't do showy jump maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the stage doesn't have much depth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so basically, you can only \Ndo horizontal movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if Elena and Jeanne come,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be impossible to let everyone \Nbe on the stage at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that Rosetta cannot perform \Nher diabolo to the fullest either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're handicapped like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just get rid of the stage roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have no choice but to do every \Npossible variation of maneuver we can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and do our best like the \Nforce of angry waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not the perfect situation, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but still, we're going to perform \Nafter doing nothing for so long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't sleep! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we'll get to see Rosetta too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't wait! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Jump, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claire, Jeanne, give me a faster tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy that everyone got together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but... I measured the stage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was smaller than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it may not be possible to let \Neveryone on stage at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, wouldn't it be nice if \Nwe could do a big maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But this time, \Nthere's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you all right being here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have so much to repay you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I'm here you can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage is quite small...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right as long \Nas we can do Diabolo Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabolo Battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about that \NDiabolo Battle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll see what I \Ncan do, and do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's practice a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure that there was \Na call to cancel the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, can you cancel that cancellation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't disassemble the stage set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can disassemble it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who called you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, but I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I bet it's Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may have to give up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if we have no choice \Nbut to give up this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After everyone was nice enough \Nto come, and even Rosetta came...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just get rid of the stage roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The roof... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but we won't get paid, \Nso I can't make anyone do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go home without doing anything. \NNot after I came here all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, from this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this entire amusement park will be our stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the customers are our audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our costumes are what we're wearing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's raise the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it will be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man running.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? They're not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, they're in \Nthe middle of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the ones who were supposed \Nto appear on the stage are going wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do, Owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh... A rose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the person you \Nmet in Theatrical Camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I asked Mia to send him an e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to drop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know he was this nice-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turned out to be better not \Nbeing able to use the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the person who \Ncancelled the show today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Kalos, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they performed on that small stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they couldn't get this kind of reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Miss Layla were here with us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.31,0:22:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is that person? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the biggest success since \Nwe opened this amusement park.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, thanks to the appearance \Nof that masked star,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}our amusement park operation \Nhas ended in success.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only that, we got a contract.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla is amazing... \NThat's what I thought, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that person is someone else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After we got a chance, we got into a pinch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We got into a pinch. We got into a pinch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, \N"The Amazing Mystery Star."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and \Non towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm here between the sky and the \Nroads, and facing against the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm facing forward so the sorrow \Ndoesn't rain down ever again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came all the way here after \NI jumped over that wall{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are many times when \NI just want to run away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm still here, so, \NI'm not daunted that much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The poem I scribbled down, I can just \Nstart writing over from the beginning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unable to write it well, I'm laughing{\i0}
